`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- The project follows a "testable seam" pattern: pure functions are exported from R3F components so they can be unit-tested without WebGL/R3F context. `NpcModel.tsx` should mirror this pattern from `TreeModel.tsx`.
- `generateNpcAppearance` in `npcAppearance.ts` already wraps `scopedRNG("npc-appearance", worldSeed, seed, role)` — `NpcModel` delegates to it rather than calling `scopedRNG` directly.
- Rules of Hooks: item slot renderers must be separate sub-components (`NpcItemGLBModel`) that are conditionally *mounted*, never conditionally *hooking*.
